The parking garage for this hotel is across the street, in a building currently under construction.	There is no valet parking, which poses a problem because they are also situated on a busy street.	Considering that hotel does not have it's own parking, but they offer the discounted rate at the parking across the street, was also a good deal.	They gladly held our bags and extended our free parking for several more hours after check out.	Leave your bags in the lobby or bring them up to your room, as you'll be parking your car in a garage across the street.